  <title>Auto-Profiles-GroundedBearing</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Definition<keyword>Grounded Bearings</keyword><keyword>Standard Bearings</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface">Grounded</text> and <text styleclass="Interface">Standard Bearing Sizes</text> relate to <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Auto-Profile">Auto-Profiles</link>. They are the <text style="font-style:italic;">default</text> diameters of circle at <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pin-Joints</text> that are added with <text styleclass="T_Menusmall">Add Auto-Profiles</text>. They are defined in the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Application-Settings" anchor="App-Auto">Application Settings dialog-box</link></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;"/></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface">Grounded Bearing</text> : arc at a <text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint</text> with the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-BasePart" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Base-Part</link>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface">Standard Bearing</text> : arc at a <text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint</text> <text style="font-weight:normal; color:#ff0000;">not</text> with the <text styleclass="Element">Base-Part</text>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
